Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:33.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:38.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 雖然這般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:50.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回憶也會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:54.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被時間之沙掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而變得曖昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:05.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}說著「命運」這詞是如此廉價
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:09.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而與我一同開懷大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:15.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:20.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定會將自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:23.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐漸忘卻在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}與你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也請留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成為無法集齊的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:38.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那無法尋覓的最後一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:43.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:49.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
